                      "default_value": "",
                      "value": "<div class=\"homeseo\">\n    <h2>Genuine Audi OEM Parts & Accessories</h2>\n<p>Genuine, Factory Audi auto parts and accessories at steeply discounted prices with available shipping to all 50 states. You can browse a full catalog of OEM parts for your <a href=\"v-audi\">Audi Model</a> and checkout without having to wait for a dealership to get back to your or answer a part form. With a full OEM catalog of parts and accessories for all Audi models, we are sure you will be able to find exactly what you need. <a href=\"/contact-us\">Contact Us</a> if you have any questions and our experts will be happy to help. Your Audi parts, on your time with Audi Parts Store!</p></div>"
